CSC 407 Project
Ethan Engert and Ezra Nagel

To run:
    python -m venv .venv
    source .venv/bin/activate
    pip install -r requirements.txt

Create mysql database if not done already:
    mysql -u root -p
    
    CREATE DATABASE yellowbox_db;
    CREATE USER 'yellowbox_user'@'localhost' IDENTIFIED BY 'password';
    GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON yellowbox_db.* TO 'yellowbox_user'@'localhost';
    FLUSH PRIVILEGES;

Run Project:
    cd yellowbox
    python flasky.py

Import Tables:

    Powershell:
        Get-Content yellowbox_db.sql | mysql -u yellowbox_user -p yellowbox_db    
    Command Line:
        mysql -u yellowbox_user -p yellowbox_db < yellowbox_db.sql
        password: password

    Command for creating .sql file: 
        mysqldump -u yellowbox_user -p yellowbox_db > yellowbox_db.sql 

Example users:
    Range from 1-15, just replace number
    Username: user1
    Password: pass1


AWS/ Docker:
    
    mysql -h yellowbox-db.c12ociym6hbt.us-east-1.rds.amazonaws.com -u admin -p -P 3306 yellowbox_db < yellowbox_db.sql

    docker build -t flasky-app .

    docker run -p 5000:5000 flasky-app



